												<div class="smalltext"><span title="Last edit: May 25, 2011, 04:42:28 PM by eMansipater" class="edited">May 10, 2011, 08:11:32 AM</span><span class="editplain"><br />Last edit: May 25, 2011, 04:42:28 PM by eMansipater</span></div><div class="smalltext"><i><span style="color:green">Merited</span> by <a href="/index.php?action=profile;u=452769">bones261</a> (1)</i></div></td>
										  <td align="right" valign="middle" height="20" style="font-size: smaller; padding-top: 4px;" class="td_buttons" ><div id="ignmsgbttns1" style="visibility: visible;">  <a class="message_number" style="vertical-align: middle;" href="https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=7815.msg114014#msg114014">#1</a>
